{"tid":1878140,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【夠買德福兩房】天鑄車位售638萬　全港住宅新高","createTime":"2020-02-13T12:06:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T23:38:59.000Z","uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9c84806209c7b6e442b8f1828c5776f9f77e0e","tid":1878140,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:06:32.000Z","msg":"樓市前景未明，車位做價仍創新高。據買賣登記資料顯示，何文田天鑄一個車位以638萬元易手，料創全港住宅車位新高紀錄。原業主於2019年3月以470萬元購入，是次轉售帳面獲利168萬元。<br />\n事實上，該屋苑車位有價有市，對上全港最貴住宅車位王亦屬其出品，做價為600萬元，是次將紀錄推高逾6.3%，售價足夠更購買九龍灣德福花園的兩房單位。<br />\n至於商業物業車位做價更瘋狂，中區商廈中環中心有車位去年以760萬元售出，創出全港最貴紀錄，至今仍未被打破。"},{"pid":"de60d7f825906e32f4e565134947049748f10893","tid":1878140,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T16:36:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200213/bkn-20200213154752193-0213_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200213%2Fbkn-20200213154752193-0213_00842_001.html&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvTyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=1331801d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200213/bkn-20200213154752193-0213_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0f08ada1d0af9b7d4c4a6178c1d0cc0b023a0a4b","tid":1878140,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T16:38:28.000Z","msg":"大陸人又走資"},{"pid":"afad640665c0afda201918edd6c83974dd002e11","tid":1878140,"uid":11040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T16:48:56.000Z","msg":"泊街算喇"},{"pid":"9e2966194ca2e842e7d699d468f7364aef1c3fd5","tid":1878140,"uid":29762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T19:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b54db4151df809f8e31b6582a071aa4d579284","tid":1878140,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike"